preference.name: CM_Block_Edits_To_Closed_Change_Objects
preference.preference_description: Gives the ability to block any edits if the change object is in a closed state. Valid Values: * true: Block edits to change objects in closed state. This is the default value. * false: Allow edits to change objects in closed state.
